GitHub Copilot

prompt: 'can you write me pseudocode for a todo app?'

result:
1. Initialize the application
    a. Create an empty list to store todos

2. Display the main menu
    a. Show options: Add Todo, View Todos, Update Todo, Delete Todo, Exit

3. Handle user input
    a. If user chooses Add Todo:
        i. Prompt for todo description
        ii. Add the new todo to the list
    b. If user chooses View Todos:
        i. Display all todos with their indices
    c. If user chooses Update Todo:
        i. Prompt for the index of the todo to update
        ii. Prompt for the new description
        iii. Update the todo at the specified index
    d. If user chooses Delete Todo:
        i. Prompt for the index of the todo to delete
        ii. Remove the todo at the specified index
    e. If user chooses Exit:
        i. End the application

4. Loop back to the main menu until the user chooses to exit